# 📂 Task Automation Tool

A Python automation utility that helps perform common file-management tasks automatically.

## 📌 Features

### Task 1: JPG File Organizer
- Finds all JPG files in the current directory
- Moves them to a specified folder
- Validates destination path

### Task 2: Email Extractor
- Reads a text file
- Extracts email addresses using Regular Expressions (Regex)
- Saves extracted emails separately

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Python 3
- OS Module
- Shutil Module
- Regular Expressions (re)

📋 Available Tasks
1️⃣ Move JPG Files
Scans the current directory
Detects all .jpg files
Moves them to a user-selected folder
2️⃣ Extract Email Addresses
Reads content from a text file
Uses Regex pattern matching
Extracts all email addresses
Saves results for future use


📚 Learning Outcomes
File handling
Directory management
Automation scripting
Regex pattern matching
Python standard libraries

